Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.94,0:00:23.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我總是被說是個迷糊的孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.10,0:00:33.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘿！你要去哪
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.57,0:00:38.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我要去中島本町的雙葉去送海苔
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.45,0:00:40.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,本來是我兄弟的工作
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.47,0:00:41.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因為他感冒了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.03,0:00:44.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,換我代替他
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.28,0:00:46.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,送
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哦 真是令人敬佩啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.26,0:00:49.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哈呀 行了行了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.92,0:00:52.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過我這是運沙石的返途 有點淩亂
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.15,0:00:57.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,送完海苔回來 還想給哥哥和妹妹買紀念品回去
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.32,0:01:00.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嚯嚯
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.30,0:01:16.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好嘞 我們已經到了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.25,0:01:19.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不要再發呆了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.37,0:01:46.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哇！耶誕節
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.84,0:01:49.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,巧克力10錢
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.56,0:01:52.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,牛奶糖大盒10錢 小盒5錢
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.64,0:01:53.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,溜溜球10錢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:53.77,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,錢：日本舊貨幣單位，100錢=1圓。此時1圓的購買力約等於如今的740円。
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.77,0:01:55.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對對 就是這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.15,0:01:59.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我想要紅的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.02,0:02:01.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還是那麼熱鬧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.93,0:02:02.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.51,0:02:05.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.86,0:02:07.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,注意腳下
Comment: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,—插曲—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:18.66,kono-op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}內心深處的天空光芒萬丈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:24.71,kono-op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}今天也遙望遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:31.91,kono-op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}流淌著眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:48.58,kono-op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}白雲向遠方飄去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:54.37,kono-op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}今天也帶著夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:03:00.69,kono-op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:06.34,kono-op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}淒淒慘慘戚戚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:12.22,kono-op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}自是人生長恨水長東
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:18.27,kono-op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}深陷無限的空虛中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:26.30,kono-op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}無可救藥
