Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後我就迷路了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,結果遇到了個長這樣的大叔
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.76,0:03:55.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.72,0:03:57.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後它說
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,用這個找路吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,把望遠鏡給我了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.30,0:04:07.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哇~看的很清楚吔
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.64,0:04:13.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,掉進的籃子裡有一個不認識的小哥
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個人是人口販子
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我們都是被拐賣的人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.12,0:04:17.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.87,0:04:20.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真倒楣
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.87,0:04:24.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我傍晚必須要給雞餵食呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.08,0:04:28.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也是今天必須和父親一起坐汽車回去
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.52,0:04:34.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也是我也是 天黑之前不回去會出大事的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,會出什麼大事呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,繼續看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大叔大叔
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.03,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊 你往裡看一下
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一到晚上就會睡著的設定
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.91,0:05:04.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,讓這傢伙連晚飯也沒得吃挺過意不去的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.19,0:05:08.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,謝謝了 浦野鈴
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.52,0:05:11.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你什麼時候知道我的名字的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,謝謝了浦野鈴
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.02,0:05:17.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂！ 別吵！
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.19,0:05:21.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我一定是犯迷糊了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.67,0:05:26.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,否則的話 那天的事一定是我的白日夢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.81,0:05:35.86,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50.193\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(337,160.618)}1935
