Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.63,0:13:47.56,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,漫畫標題為《鬼哥哥從軍記》
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.22,0:13:43.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,於東太平洋全海域作戰中的帝國海軍部隊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,萬歲 萬歲
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,萬歲
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.35,0:13:52.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,森田家的侄女 這邊早點採比較好哦

Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.01,0:13:54.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.73,0:13:58.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,挺棒的決戰服嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.62,0:14:03.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.17,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,越做越好了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.78,0:14:20.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也正好了 那來吃午飯
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.72,0:14:23.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好遠
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.47,0:14:24.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.42,0:14:27.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴姐會嫁到好遠的地方去
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.50,0:14:29.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,澄姐就很近
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.75,0:14:37.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,筷子拿得比較遠的人會嫁到遠處
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,奶奶是從哪嫁過來的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是從古江嫁過來的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.06,0:14:47.93,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,古江：廣島市地名。\n草津：廣島市地名，與古江相鄰。
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,從隔壁的古江到草津都這樣了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.05,0:14:51.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那嫁到滿洲等地方的人豈不是火筷子都不夠長了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.05,0:14:51.70,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,滿洲：指「滿洲國」所在地。九一八事變後日軍佔領中國東北並在當地扶植傀儡政權「滿州國」，其所在地日本國內稱之為「滿州」。
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.75,0:14:55.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你一邊這麼說卻一邊拿遠了筷子
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.03,0:14:58.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嫁太近不就沒什麼追求了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 馬上回去
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.85,0:15:07.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,接了個電話 我還以為是什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.69,0:15:10.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有人到你家說要娶你了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.00,0:15:12.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,專門從吳市過來
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.54,0:15:13.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吳市？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.17,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,吳市：廣島縣市名，距廣島市約20公里。\N為二戰時於日本帝國海軍第2海軍區鎮守府（吳鎮守府）所在地成立。
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.63,0:15:17.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 你幾歲了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.09,0:15:18.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,19
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.61,0:15:21.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周歲的話18
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不喜歡的話拒絕就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,稍微過去看一下
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.65,0:15:28.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 稍微過來一下
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.65,0:15:34.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,為了你總有一天會成為新娘而準備的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.72,0:15:38.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,能合身就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.48,0:15:47.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後要和那邊辦婚禮對吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.04,0:15:54.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那天晚上新郎會問你「帶傘了嗎」
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.14,0:15:59.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後你就說「帶了一把新的」
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.38,0:16:03.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後如果他說「可以給我嗎」
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.98,0:16:06.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你就說「請便」 聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.03,0:16:07.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒有為什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.45,0:16:11.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我好像要成為大人了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.51,0:16:16.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,說到吳市的話 就是有軍港的地方吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.69,0:16:19.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有很多水兵
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.77,0:16:25.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水原
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.51,0:16:30.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,快點回家去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.99,0:16:31.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.80,0:16:35.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你的媽媽嚇了一跳 在吵吵鬧鬧的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.24,0:16:36.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鄰居都知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嚇死了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.65,0:16:42.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我差點以為是你
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.71,0:16:43.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你傻嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.62,0:16:48.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是因為哥哥七周年忌辰這個莊重的理由回來的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.83,0:16:53.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不認識對方嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.11,0:16:54.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不認識
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.65,0:16:58.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,可能是把我和澄弄錯了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,澄也比較漂亮
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.42,0:17:04.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我倒覺得不是這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.29,0:17:08.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,他是在這邊的學校上學的時候
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.19,0:17:10.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不知道在哪遇到的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.88,0:17:14.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,為了找到你們真是費了好大力
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.07,0:17:18.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我家也因為三年前江波沖町的填海造路
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.61,0:17:20.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不再採海苔了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.07,0:17:20.68,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,江波沖町：廣島市江波所屬町，距草津約4km
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.97,0:17:24.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過應該可以恢復以前的樣子了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.31,0:17:28.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,雖然我也不知道到底是不是好事
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.50,0:17:33.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過感覺口中有牛奶糖的味道 是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.08,0:17:35.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.24,0:17:37.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,難辦了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.79,0:17:41.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,雖然說不喜歡也可以拒絕
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過我也不知道我喜不喜歡他
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.73,0:17:45.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.02,0:17:47.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.64,0:17:51.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我們迷路了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,電車站是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在這邊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.25,0:17:56.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.60,0:17:59.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,雖然有個親切的水兵告訴了我
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.91,0:18:04.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,他也是個很稀奇的人
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.53,0:18:09.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好像在山中給個很稀奇的女性帶路平安回去了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.68,0:18:16.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我真的有那麼迷糊嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.01,0:18:16.43,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50.193\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(337,160.618)\3c&H868686&}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.01,0:18:16.43,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(313,208.803)\3c&H868686&}年
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.01,0:18:16.43,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60.232\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(335,303.166)\3c&H868686&}2
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.01,0:18:16.43,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(309,348.565)\3c&H868686&}月
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼時候變成這樣的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.36,0:18:29.39,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,站牌所示的列車路線為：廣島站出發（山陽本線），經海田市站（轉吳線），矢野站，坂站，小屋浦站。
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.55,0:18:32.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.75,0:18:37.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,接下來請將靠海一側的百葉窗關上
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哪裡的窗開著
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.27,0:18:56.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吳 吳
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.55,0:19:00.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是海軍們的砲台訓練吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真的不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我覺得很適合哦
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.70,0:19:23.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,木炭巴士不會開上來對吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.83,0:19:24.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 小林夫人
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.93,0:19:30.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小林夫人 今天就拜託了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.25,0:19:32.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,天氣也不錯真是太好了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.99,0:19:36.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今後承您照顧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小女子不才 今後會盡孝的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是周作的伯母小林
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.62,0:19:43.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是作為你們的媒人
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.92,0:19:46.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,她到底知不知道自己將來嫁給的人的名字
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.92,0:19:49.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真的不才啊 到底行不行啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.91,0:20:00.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要走上來這麼高啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這裡是附近最角落的地方了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.15,0:20:04.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.07,0:20:06.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,過來了哦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.36,0:20:10.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在這個年代萬事都要從簡非常抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我家的孩子有點怯場
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.12,0:20:13.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.74,0:20:14.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.01,0:20:17.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,難得好看的衣服要白費了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.62,0:20:22.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂 鈴 你在哪裡脫衣服啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.75,0:20:31.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這還真是豐盛呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這孩子的哥哥沒能來真是太可惜了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.80,0:20:37.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真的來了不少人呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.56,0:20:42.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吃多點 這可是把晚上的份也拿出來了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.87,0:20:45.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這個燉菜煮的很好嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.73,0:20:49.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,太好了呢 是個挺老實的人
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒人會在這種場合亂來吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不就亂來了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.49,0:20:58.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那回娘家的時候再見了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.32,0:21:00.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好 再見
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.25,0:21:03.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我還會再來的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.23,0:21:12.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個…是誰來著
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,新娘也嫁過來了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.92,0:21:17.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,家裡的事都交給她 你就悠閒地睡吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.55,0:21:18.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.04,0:21:24.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸 媽媽 今後就承您們照顧了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.45,0:21:26.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不 我們才是
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.96,0:21:29.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我的腳一直疼
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.94,0:21:32.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就拜託你了 鈴
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.73,0:21:33.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.68,0:21:35.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.13,0:21:38.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,徑子煮飯老是會焦掉
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.89,0:21:43.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 那個是嫁走了的姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.75,0:22:03.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是軍艦的照射訓練
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.64,0:22:08.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我到底是從哪邊過來的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.53,0:22:18.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,被子 謝謝你幫我鋪好了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.11,0:22:19.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.47,0:22:25.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對了 鈴
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.13,0:22:26.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.01,0:22:30.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,帶傘了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.62,0:22:38.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是 帶了一把新的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.63,0:22:41.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,稍微借我一下
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.45,0:22:49.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.63,0:22:52.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.96,0:22:58.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 還是澀的
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.67,0:23:03.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你 白天的時候什麼都沒吃對吧
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.12,0:23:07.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原來你會好好用嘴巴吃飯 我放心了
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.95,0:23:10.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,放心吧放心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.61,0:23:12.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,剛剛連種子都吞下去了
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.71,0:23:13.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好好從嘴巴吃的
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.04,0:23:17.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.23,0:23:19.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我們以前 在哪裡見過嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.60,0:23:24.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,見過哦 你不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.45,0:23:28.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起 我本來就比較迷糊
Dialogue: 1,0:23:28.48,0:23:30.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你從以前開始就是這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.56,0:23:35.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後 以前也是 這裡有顆黑痣
Dialogue: 1,0:24:08.63,0:24:12.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,水井在下面 是和鄰居共用的
Dialogue: 1,0:24:12.38,0:24:12.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 1,0:24:38.56,0:24:43.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,北…條…
Dialogue: 1,0:24:50.93,0:24:52.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 1,0:24:52.77,0:24:58.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這裡是吳市的什麼町的幾號來著
Dialogue: 1,0:24:59.98,0:25:00.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:25:00.77,0:25:01.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那再見
Dialogue: 1,0:25:02.51,0:25:03.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 1,0:25:05.28,0:25:09.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這附近的人都是當海軍的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:25:19.52,0:25:20.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,北條夫人
Dialogue: 1,0:25:24.44,0:25:25.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,北條夫人
Dialogue: 1,0:25:25.77,0:25:26.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 1,0:25:26.92,0:25:30.97,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正稚艺_GBK\fs55.212\frz257.7\c&H777B7D&\pos(1208,620.386)}二月二十四日的配給值班
Dialogue: 1,0:25:26.92,0:25:30.97,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正稚艺_GBK\fs55.212\frz257.7\c&H777B7D&\pos(1070,596.293)}知多 北條 刈谷
Dialogue: 1,0:25:26.92,0:25:30.97,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正稚艺_GBK\fs55.212\frz257.7\c&H777B7D&\pos(914,560.154)}例會的通知
Dialogue: 1,0:25:26.92,0:25:30.97,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正稚艺_GBK\fs45.174\frz257.7\c&H777B7D&\pos(776.032,582.208)}二十四日（星期四）午後七點
Dialogue: 1,0:25:26.92,0:25:30.97,kono-hmz,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正稚艺_GBK\fs45.174\c&H777B7D&\frz255\pos(669.845,541.61)}於中長之木領保館
Dialogue: 1,0:25:26.90,0:25:30.91,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,鄰保館：在有貧困、教育、歧視和環境等比較惡劣的問題的區域，擁有解決這些問題的專門知識的人常駐，\n　　　　對當地人進行適當的援助的社會福利設施。
Dialogue: 1,0:25:27.12,0:25:28.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,配給的值班？
Dialogue: 1,0:25:28.53,0:25:33.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這個和這個 一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:25:33.63,0:25:35.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,承您照顧了
Dialogue: 1,0:25:35.37,0:25:36.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是知多
Dialogue: 1,0:25:36.14,0:25:37.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是刈穀
Dialogue: 1,0:25:36.14,0:25:37.13,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,刈：音同「易」，割。
Dialogue: 1,0:25:42.38,0:25:43.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂 你又這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:25:43.73,0:25:45.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我不是好好量著嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:25:45.93,0:25:47.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不是按目測來的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:25:47.97,0:25:48.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 1,0:25:48.67,0:25:49.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,會不公平的
Dialogue: 1,0:25:49.86,0:25:51.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 1,0:25:51.17,0:25:52.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 1,0:25:52.45,0:25:53.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:25:53.50,0:25:56.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你就是這個地方不行
Dialogue: 1,0:25:56.27,0:25:57.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哪點
Dialogue: 1,0:25:57.93,0:25:59.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我還年輕
Dialogue: 1,0:25:59.64,0:26:01.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要掉下來了
Dialogue: 1,0:26:08.31,0:26:09.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,0:26:09.99,0:26:12.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,必須指出其威力非常之大
Dialogue: 1,0:26:13.46,0:26:15.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果燃燒彈被投放的話
Dialogue: 1,0:26:11.40,0:26:14.00,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,瓩：舊日本單位合字，意為“千克”。（已棄用）
Dialogue: 1,0:26:15.89,0:26:19.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,首先必要的是隨機應變
Dialogue: 1,0:26:20.26,0:26:22.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再靠近點吧
Dialogue: 1,0:26:22.84,0:26:24.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這個座位可是很冷的
Dialogue: 1,0:26:26.19,0:26:26.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:26:28.47,0:26:31.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這些就是我的日常
Dialogue: 1,0:26:32.09,0:26:37.56,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50.193\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(337,160.618)}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:26:32.09,0:26:37.56,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(313,208.803)}年
Dialogue: 1,0:26:32.09,0:26:37.56,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60.232\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(335,303.166)}3
Dialogue: 1,0:26:32.09,0:26:37.56,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(309,348.565)}月
Dialogue: 1,0:26:42.67,0:26:46.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 那是徑子還沒出嫁前的衣服
Dialogue: 1,0:26:46.42,0:26:47.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那件也放倉庫裡吧
Dialogue: 1,0:26:48.54,0:26:52.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,她和未婚夫出去的時候就會穿這件衣服
Dialogue: 1,0:26:53.24,0:26:57.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,去看電影 吃洋食 看博覽會
Dialogue: 1,0:27:00.32,0:27:03.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐是個摩登女郎啊
Dialogue: 1,0:27:04.03,0:27:06.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那時候還不是現在這樣的年代
Dialogue: 1,0:27:07.77,0:27:09.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作四年級的時候
Dialogue: 1,0:27:09.86,0:27:13.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,為了和平的軍力縮減導致造不了軍艦
Dialogue: 1,0:27:09.86,0:27:13.61,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,注：指的是《華盛頓海軍條約》
Dialogue: 1,0:27:14.85,0:27:18.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我們家和這附近的人大多失業了
Dialogue: 1,0:27:18.85,0:27:20.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是不得了
Dialogue: 1,0:27:21.21,0:27:23.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,徑子就是那樣的孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:27:23.44,0:27:27.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,工作也是自己決定 丈夫也是自己找
Dialogue: 1,0:27:29.29,0:27:32.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,既然如此我也要不認輸地努力工作了
Dialogue: 1,0:27:33.96,0:27:37.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個時候真是不得了
Dialogue: 1,0:27:37.68,0:27:38.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,萬歲
Dialogue: 1,0:27:38.58,0:27:41.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是懷念的不得了的那個時候
Dialogue: 1,0:27:50.82,0:27:52.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 你好
Dialogue: 1,0:27:53.52,0:27:54.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 1,0:27:54.75,0:27:57.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 歡迎回來 姐姐
Dialogue: 1,0:28:00.78,0:28:01.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,簡樸
Dialogue: 1,0:28:04.08,0:28:07.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,簡樸什麼的 現在大米也是挺貴重的東西
Dialogue: 1,0:28:07.96,0:28:08.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是說你
Dialogue: 1,0:28:10.08,0:28:13.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你是廣島來的 我還以為你有多上流
Dialogue: 1,0:28:13.91,0:28:16.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你那縫縫補補的褲子是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 1,0:28:17.18,0:28:18.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你在炒豆子嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:28:19.06,0:28:21.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎呀 晴美 歡迎來哦
Dialogue: 1,0:28:21.71,0:28:24.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,媽媽經常會心情不好
Dialogue: 1,0:28:25.22,0:28:26.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以晴美有乖哦
Dialogue: 1,0:28:26.78,0:28:30.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起 我現在只有這件
Dialogue: 1,0:28:30.16,0:28:31.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再做一件 馬上
Dialogue: 1,0:28:35.84,0:28:37.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還有那袋大米不是禮物
Dialogue: 1,0:28:38.16,0:28:39.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是我和女兒的份
Dialogue: 1,0:28:42.05,0:28:43.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後 徑子
Dialogue: 1,0:28:43.82,0:28:45.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你聽我說啦 媽媽
Dialogue: 1,0:28:45.39,0:28:48.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎呀 現在難辦了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:28:50.31,0:28:50.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:28:51.19,0:28:53.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你又來了 錯了錯了
Dialogue: 1,0:28:53.90,0:28:57.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你這麼笨可是嫁不出去的
Dialogue: 1,0:28:57.47,0:28:59.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不管了 我不嫁了
Dialogue: 1,0:29:06.79,0:29:09.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個 腰的地方是
Dialogue: 1,0:29:11.03,0:29:12.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 原來如此
Dialogue: 1,0:29:27.92,0:29:29.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,把這個解開
Dialogue: 1,0:29:30.52,0:29:31.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再裁剪一下
Dialogue: 1,0:29:32.44,0:29:34.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,合在一起 縫起來
Dialogue: 1,0:29:35.75,0:29:38.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,穿上橡皮筋就做好了
Dialogue: 1,0:29:38.54,0:29:39.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 1,0:29:43.15,0:29:44.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是黑村晴美
Dialogue: 1,0:29:44.69,0:29:46.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是北條鈴 你好
Dialogue: 1,0:29:48.19,0:29:50.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 給我繩子
Dialogue: 1,0:29:51.13,0:29:52.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這個可以嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:30:09.98,0:30:11.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 你去買東西嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:30:12.08,0:30:13.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對 去配給所
Dialogue: 1,0:30:14.29,0:30:17.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我去吧 配給票和錢包給我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:30:18.32,0:30:20.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎 拜託了
Dialogue: 1,0:30:35.13,0:30:36.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 1,0:30:41.63,0:30:43.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,夠了 我來做
Dialogue: 1,0:30:52.84,0:30:55.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我說 媽媽
Dialogue: 1,0:30:57.33,0:30:58.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 1,0:30:59.06,0:30:59.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 1,0:30:59.89,0:31:01.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就是湯的料來著
Dialogue: 1,0:31:19.93,0:31:22.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,徑子和晴美來了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:31:23.28,0:31:24.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,兩個人嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:31:24.31,0:31:25.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 父親
Dialogue: 1,0:31:25.87,0:31:27.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在這裡多待一會吧
Dialogue: 1,0:31:29.73,0:31:34.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真少見 姐姐燒的飯居然沒怎麼燒焦
Dialogue: 1,0:31:34.65,0:31:36.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你說什麼 周作
Dialogue: 1,0:31:36.32,0:31:38.68,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:31:36.57,0:31:38.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個 姐姐
Dialogue: 1,0:31:39.09,0:31:42.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,多虧了你的幫忙 和服改好了
Dialogue: 1,0:31:43.31,0:31:45.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:31:45.60,0:31:47.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因為母親的腳也不是很方便
Dialogue: 1,0:31:48.36,0:31:52.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,像你這樣的孩子突然間被帶到一個陌生的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:31:52.76,0:31:55.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要是我一直待在這裡就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:31:57.22,0:32:00.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 你不如回廣島吧
Dialogue: 1,0:32:03.63,0:32:04.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那樣也好
Dialogue: 1,0:32:10.24,0:32:11.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 1,0:32:11.99,0:32:13.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好累呀
Dialogue: 1,0:32:13.71,0:32:14.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 1,0:32:15.74,0:32:17.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,已經八點了
Dialogue: 1,0:32:17.77,0:32:19.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今天也很多呀
Dialogue: 1,0:32:21.07,0:32:22.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這全都是千人針嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:32:21.07,0:32:22.66,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,注：為了祝願出征軍人保命免災，由一千個女人,在一塊白布上,用紅線每人各縫一針製成的腰帶
Dialogue: 1,0:32:22.69,0:32:25.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是呀 澄 等下你也要幫忙縫一下
Dialogue: 1,0:32:27.00,0:32:28.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂鈴 該起來了
Dialogue: 1,0:32:29.62,0:32:30.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:32:33.18,0:32:34.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,拿著 該吃晚飯了
Dialogue: 1,0:32:35.89,0:32:40.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嚇死我了 我做了一個遠嫁吳市的夢
Dialogue: 1,0:32:42.49,0:32:44.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,醒來了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:32:43.54,0:32:44.13,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,醒了
Dialogue: 1,0:32:44.79,0:32:48.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後 姐姐就跟我說讓我回廣島去
Dialogue: 1,0:32:49.98,0:32:52.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我就在想這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 1,0:32:52.47,0:32:53.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 回娘家呀
Dialogue: 1,0:32:54.67,0:32:56.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後公公婆婆就說
Dialogue: 1,0:32:57.23,0:32:59.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,「一直以來沒注意到你的想法真的很抱歉」
Dialogue: 1,0:33:00.67,0:33:03.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,「回去好好休息兩三天吧」
Dialogue: 1,0:33:04.12,0:33:04.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐也說
Dialogue: 1,0:33:06.63,0:33:09.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,既然你都這樣說了 也挺好的不是麼
Dialogue: 1,0:33:10.92,0:33:13.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,說起來 給要一寄了明信片沒有
Dialogue: 1,0:33:13.51,0:33:14.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我嗎 已經寄了
Dialogue: 1,0:33:15.40,0:33:17.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但…還沒有回覆
Dialogue: 1,0:33:18.74,0:33:20.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,家裡也是嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:33:22.59,0:33:23.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 畢竟這麼遠
Dialogue: 1,0:33:23.91,0:33:25.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,畢竟鬼哥哥不愛動筆
Dialogue: 1,0:33:26.57,0:33:29.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也可能是鈴把地址寫錯了
Dialogue: 1,0:33:30.55,0:33:32.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,洗澡去 洗澡去
Dialogue: 1,0:33:32.81,0:33:34.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,澄在挺身隊那邊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 1,0:33:32.81,0:33:34.84,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,注：挺身隊是根據1944年8月頒佈的法令組成的女子勞工隊。
Dialogue: 1,0:33:34.85,0:33:36.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,基本上習慣了
Dialogue: 1,0:33:36.49,0:33:38.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我全身都是機油臭味對吧
Dialogue: 1,0:33:39.21,0:33:42.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那都是些危險的工作 真辛苦你了
Dialogue: 1,0:33:42.34,0:33:45.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,雖說如此 但也沒有做海苔那樣寒冷
Dialogue: 1,0:33:45.46,0:33:46.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也是有好事情發生的
Dialogue: 1,0:33:47.07,0:33:51.72,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,注：將校泛指少尉以上的軍官
Dialogue: 1,0:33:47.07,0:33:51.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有個很帥的將校先生偷偷地把食堂的食券塞給我
Dialogue: 1,0:33:51.72,0:33:52.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 1,0:33:53.05,0:33:55.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒想到一不小心知道了陸軍的秘密了
Dialogue: 1,0:33:56.15,0:33:57.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴呢 你怎麼樣
Dialogue: 1,0:33:58.25,0:33:59.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吳市那有什麼好事發生嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:34:01.40,0:34:03.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要記的東西有很多 所以還沒有
Dialogue: 1,0:34:05.56,0:34:09.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我好像一不小心
Dialogue: 1,0:34:09.09,0:34:12.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,觸碰到了海軍的秘密
Dialogue: 1,0:34:12.28,0:34:13.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:34:13.21,0:34:13.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,快睡吧
Dialogue: 1,0:34:16.44,0:34:17.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,0:34:17.67,0:34:18.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:34:19.14,0:34:21.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你貌似有點禿了
Dialogue: 1,0:34:24.11,0:34:27.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再見 鈴 我出門了
Dialogue: 1,0:34:28.04,0:34:29.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,根據戰時特殊措施
Dialogue: 1,0:34:30.07,0:34:33.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,等到下個月 短期外出也會受到限制
Dialogue: 1,0:34:34.16,0:34:35.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,請多保重
Dialogue: 1,0:34:36.62,0:34:39.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也要去婦人會那裡幫忙了
Dialogue: 1,0:34:39.65,0:34:42.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,媽媽也要出門嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:34:57.24,0:35:00.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,爸爸給了我一些零用錢
Dialogue: 1,0:35:32.35,0:35:33.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 1,0:35:35.25,0:35:36.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再見了 廣島
Dialogue: 1,0:35:41.52,0:35:43.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正少儿_gbk\fs40.154\bord0\c&H6C6F73&\frz275.7\pos(1070.506,462.013)}今天的車票已經全部{\c&H6F75AA&}賣光
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.52,0:35:43.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正少儿_gbk\fs40.154\bord0\c&H6C6F73&\frz275.7\pos(747.036,344.672)}廣島站
Dialogue: 1,0:35:43.27,0:35:45.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後你就回來了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:35:45.85,0:35:48.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對他們家實在是太不好意思了
Dialogue: 1,0:35:56.54,0:35:58.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 1,0:35:58.99,0:36:05.08,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50.193\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(337,160.618)\3c&H868686&}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:35:58.99,0:36:05.08,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(313,208.803)\3c&H868686&}年
Dialogue: 1,0:35:58.99,0:36:05.08,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60.232\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(335,303.166)\3c&H868686&}4
Dialogue: 1,0:35:58.99,0:36:05.08,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(309,348.565)\3c&H868686&}月
Dialogue: 1,0:36:00.36,0:36:02.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐她一直都在家裡
Dialogue: 1,0:36:06.64,0:36:07.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 1,0:36:08.14,0:36:09.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,借一下硯臺給我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:36:10.15,0:36:11.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,為啥 晴美
Dialogue: 1,0:36:12.44,0:36:13.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,借給我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:36:14.52,0:36:17.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 你跟晴美說什麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:36:19.94,0:36:22.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我能把傳閱板給下一家了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:36:23.19,0:36:24.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:36:25.74,0:36:26.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 1,0:36:27.17,0:36:30.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,自從從廣島回來後就一直這個樣子了
Dialogue: 1,0:36:31.27,0:36:33.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,由她去吧 她還只是個孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:36:33.27,0:36:35.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 1,0:36:37.60,0:36:39.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我都說了不可以
Dialogue: 1,0:36:39.46,0:36:40.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,借給我吧
Dialogue: 1,0:36:41.16,0:36:43.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你根本不需要這個吧
Dialogue: 1,0:37:08.18,0:37:09.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 1,0:37:11.02,0:37:12.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在摘野草啊
Dialogue: 1,0:37:14.27,0:37:16.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我想著摘一些來當晚飯的配菜
Dialogue: 1,0:37:18.58,0:37:21.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這附近的蒲公英都是白色的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:37:21.90,0:37:23.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,江波那邊的不一樣麼
Dialogue: 1,0:37:24.32,0:37:26.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也有些黃色的呢
Dialogue: 1,0:37:29.46,0:37:31.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,可能是從很遙遠的地方來的
Dialogue: 1,0:37:33.64,0:37:36.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 我見你沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 1,0:37:36.63,0:37:38.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原來是思念家鄉了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:37:38.60,0:37:39.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 1,0:37:46.30,0:37:47.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,快看那邊
Dialogue: 1,0:37:48.27,0:37:49.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今天還有航空母艦呢
Dialogue: 1,0:37:50.40,0:37:52.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,應該是飛鷹和隼鷹吧
Dialogue: 1,0:37:50.40,0:37:52.26,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,飛鷹、隼鷹：均為飛鷹級航空母艦，於1943年底修復損傷後泊於吳港。
Dialogue: 1,0:37:52.41,0:37:53.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真大
Dialogue: 1,0:37:55.03,0:37:57.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後在那邊小小的都是驅逐艦
Dialogue: 1,0:37:57.69,0:37:59.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,連德國進口的U型潛艇也有
Dialogue: 1,0:37:57.69,0:37:59.68,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,U型潛艇：指德國U-511號潛艇，渡讓給日本後做反潛訓練艦泊於吳港。
Dialogue: 1,0:38:00.05,0:38:03.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,而那個看起來很普通的船是潛水母艦
Dialogue: 1,0:38:00.05,0:38:03.40,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,潛水母艦：潛艇的水上補給艦。此艦應為與U-511同屬吳潛水艦隊的迅鯨號。
Dialogue: 1,0:38:08.31,0:38:10.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,看 繡眼鳥在天上飛
Dialogue: 1,0:38:11.26,0:38:13.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在那裡 那裡 快看
Dialogue: 1,0:38:13.59,0:38:14.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我看到了
Dialogue: 1,0:38:17.07,0:38:20.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作 那是什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:38:20.60,0:38:22.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是船嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:38:22.53,0:38:23.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個是大和
Dialogue: 1,0:38:24.57,0:38:28.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,產自東洋第一的軍港 世界第一的軍艦
Dialogue: 1,0:38:22.53,0:38:28.13,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,大和：大和號戰列艦，建造於吳海軍工廠。
Dialogue: 1,0:38:28.95,0:38:31.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在那艘船上也載有人嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:38:32.06,0:38:32.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:38:35.91,0:38:37.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大概有兩千七百人
Dialogue: 1,0:38:37.74,0:38:39.82,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,注意前行 注意前行
Dialogue: 1,0:38:40.87,0:38:43.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,兩千七百人
Dialogue: 1,0:38:44.21,0:38:45.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:38:45.72,0:38:48.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 對他們說「歡迎回來吳市」吧
Dialogue: 1,0:38:50.59,0:38:54.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,每天都要在那樣的地方給這麼多人煮飯嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:38:54.77,0:38:55.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,0:38:55.28,0:38:56.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那洗衣服呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:39:01.74,0:39:04.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 1,0:39:04.68,0:39:05.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 1,0:39:06.26,0:39:07.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 1,0:39:17.37,0:39:18.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我說啊 鈴
Dialogue: 1,0:39:18.90,0:39:21.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,太過於在意的話 禿頭只會變得越來越嚴重的啦
Dialogue: 1,0:39:22.00,0:39:23.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,被你發現了呀
Dialogue: 1,0:39:24.22,0:39:26.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,借我筆吧
Dialogue: 1,0:39:26.31,0:39:29.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我想幫鈴阿姨的頭上塗下墨水
Dialogue: 1,0:39:29.22,0:39:30.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我說了不行
Dialogue: 1,0:39:30.60,0:39:33.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不是已經把那一片都弄黑了嗎
Comment: 0,0:39:34.62,0:39:38.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,#0
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.38,0:39:46.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這些是在配給站拿到的小松菜種子
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.09,0:39:50.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這可是東京的蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.89,0:39:52.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,種到地裡就能發芽
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.23,0:39:58.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這種粗活你最拿手了 對吧鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.11,0:40:00.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.27,0:40:01.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.69,0:40:05.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,趕緊種到地裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.61,0:40:10.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,直到勝利那一天...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.66,0:40:12.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,直到...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.61,0:40:12.41,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,注：曲名為「直至勝利日」，是1944年由古賀政男作曲的戰時歌謠
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.79,0:40:15.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美 你也來一起種吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.65,0:40:49.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,試驗種植就先弄到這裡 現在就去種到自家地裡
Dialogue: 1,0:40:41.65,0:40:50.57,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,也沒個大人樣 居然跟六歲孩子較勁 真給周作丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.74,0:40:53.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,媽媽 那是大和
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.87,0:40:57.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那艘煙囪像神主帽子的是隼鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.87,0:40:57.62,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,神主：日本神社的神職人員。
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.75,0:40:59.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還有巡洋艦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.58,0:41:02.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那是愛宕？還是摩耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.59,0:41:04.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.58,0:41:04.05,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,愛宕、摩耶：均為高雄型重巡洋艦。\N1944年4月時，愛宕方於橫須賀修復完成，而摩耶泊於太平洋上的林加泊地，二者皆不在吳港。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.63,0:41:09.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.64,0:41:16.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,回去吧 晴美
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.06,0:41:24.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐突然就回了婆家 怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.57,0:41:30.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,難道說姐夫是在軍艦上服役
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.07,0:41:34.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,她是睹物思人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.16,0:41:43.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好了 我也要認真去準備煮飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.17,0:41:48.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,武運昌隆
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.68,0:41:59.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,該準備煮飯了 正當我這麼想的時候 配給量卻已經大量減少
Comment: 0,0:41:59.89,0:42:04.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,#1
Dialogue: 1,0:41:55.87,0:42:00.62,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50.193\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(337,160.618)\3c&H868686&}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:41:55.87,0:42:00.62,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(313,208.803)\3c&H868686&}年
Dialogue: 1,0:41:55.87,0:42:00.62,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60.232\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(335,303.166)\3c&H868686&}5
Dialogue: 1,0:41:55.87,0:42:00.62,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(309,348.565)\3c&H868686&}月
Dialogue: 1,0:41:59.96,0:42:04.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,四條沙丁魚乾要做為一家四口三餐的量
Dialogue: 1,0:42:05.42,0:42:07.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 也比只有青菜葉的日子還要好
Dialogue: 1,0:42:08.17,0:42:11.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在這裡排隊的話總能買到豆腐渣的
Dialogue: 1,0:42:07.75,0:42:11.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正少兒_gbk\fs40.154\bord0\c&H6C6F73&\pos(629.058,672.891)}今天有豆腐渣
Dialogue: 1,0:42:12.34,0:42:13.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 1,0:42:15.26,0:42:19.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,堇菜 繁縷 杉菜
Dialogue: 1,0:42:19.85,0:42:25.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,蒲公英 酢漿草 沙丁魚乾 豆腐渣 馬鈴薯 紅薯
Dialogue: 1,0:42:25.61,0:42:27.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小麥粉 梅乾的種子
Dialogue: 1,0:42:30.57,0:42:33.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,先把紅薯切開 蒸煮
Dialogue: 1,0:42:33.57,0:42:36.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,輕微燙一下杉菜 晾乾水分後切碎
Dialogue: 1,0:42:36.95,0:42:39.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,用小麥粉把芋頭和杉菜混合起來
Dialogue: 1,0:42:39.70,0:42:40.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,簡單揉成團
Dialogue: 1,0:42:41.12,0:42:42.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,中午飯就這樣做好啦
Dialogue: 1,0:42:42.92,0:42:45.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,徑子她們不在就顯得好安靜呢
Dialogue: 1,0:42:45.58,0:42:47.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,剩下的就曬乾保存起來
Dialogue: 1,0:42:49.46,0:42:50.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,接下來還有
Dialogue: 1,0:42:51.42,0:42:54.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,用五倍的水來把米煮成稀飯
Dialogue: 1,0:42:55.59,0:42:58.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,加入馬鈴薯切塊再煮上十分鐘
Dialogue: 1,0:42:59.81,0:43:01.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,隨後加切碎的繁縷
Dialogue: 1,0:43:02.52,0:43:05.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,蘿蔔皮 蒲公英的根部
Dialogue: 1,0:43:05.35,0:43:07.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,細切成絲後加入砂糖和醬油燉煮
Dialogue: 1,0:43:08.69,0:43:10.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,加上切碎的蒲公英葉子
Dialogue: 1,0:43:11.15,0:43:13.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,最後加入豆腐渣燉煮
Dialogue: 1,0:43:15.41,0:43:19.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,蘿蔔切薄 加入鹽和酢漿草混勻
Dialogue: 1,0:43:21.12,0:43:23.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,把梅乾的種子和水放入鍋中
Dialogue: 1,0:43:23.66,0:43:26.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,當沸騰的時候再加入沙丁魚乾
Dialogue: 1,0:43:26.63,0:43:29.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不要蓋上蓋子 不停用湯汁澆在上面
Dialogue: 1,0:43:29.42,0:43:31.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,煮好後放鹽調味
Dialogue: 1,0:43:31.42,0:43:34.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這個是刈谷教的做法
Dialogue: 1,0:43:35.01,0:43:37.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是大米的配給只有一半而已
Dialogue: 1,0:43:37.76,0:43:39.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以只能吃放多點芋頭做的稀飯
Dialogue: 1,0:43:39.60,0:43:40.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 1,0:43:40.60,0:43:42.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,接下來 明天也包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 1,0:43:43.56,0:43:46.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這是忠臣楠木公為了固守城池時撐更久
Dialogue: 1,0:43:43.56,0:43:46.35,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,楠木公：楠木正成，鐮倉幕府末期到南北朝時期著名武將
Dialogue: 1,0:43:46.56,0:43:49.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,而發明出的糧食增量法
Dialogue: 1,0:43:51.32,0:43:53.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,首先 把大米仔細翻炒
Dialogue: 1,0:43:55.07,0:43:58.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,加入三倍的水量 用小火慢慢煮透
Dialogue: 1,0:44:00.58,0:44:03.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不僅要節省大米的用量還要節省燃料
Dialogue: 1,0:44:04.54,0:44:09.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這時就要交給大日本帝國的利器 無火爐灶了
Dialogue: 1,0:44:04.54,0:44:09.67,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,無火爐灶（火なしこんろ）：一種利用熱鍋中餘熱進行加熱的炊具。
Dialogue: 1,0:44:10.63,0:44:11.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,等待過夜
Dialogue: 1,0:44:15.05,0:44:18.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,利用隔夜的煮魚湯汁並加入堇菜
Dialogue: 1,0:44:18.64,0:44:20.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,拌入味噌直至煮沸
Dialogue: 1,0:44:21.26,0:44:24.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,再次點火煮沸米飯
Dialogue: 1,0:44:24.85,0:44:25.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 1,0:44:26.44,0:44:29.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這就是源自楠木公的楠公飯了
Dialogue: 1,0:44:30.65,0:44:32.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這邊是給父親做的便當
Dialogue: 1,0:44:35.53,0:44:37.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今早的飯量還真是多呢
Dialogue: 1,0:44:37.70,0:44:39.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,飯粒全都膨脹起來了
Dialogue: 1,0:44:39.66,0:44:41.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原來還有這樣的做法呢
Dialogue: 1,0:44:42.03,0:44:42.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:44:42.70,0:44:44.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 1,0:44:54.92,0:44:55.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 1,0:44:55.55,0:44:56.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 1,0:44:56.55,0:44:59.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那樣子也能吃得這麼香的楠木公
Dialogue: 1,0:44:59.84,0:45:02.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一定是一位了不起的豪傑呢
Dialogue: 1,0:45:03.31,0:45:04.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 1,0:45:05.92,0:45:11.25,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50.193\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(337,160.618)}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:45:05.92,0:45:11.25,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(313,208.803)}年
Dialogue: 1,0:45:05.92,0:45:11.25,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60.232\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(335,303.166)}6
Dialogue: 1,0:45:05.92,0:45:11.25,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(309,348.565)}月
Dialogue: 1,0:45:27.52,0:45:31.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,警戒警報發出
Dialogue: 1,0:45:32.48,0:45:35.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,空襲警報發出
Dialogue: 1,0:45:42.41,0:45:44.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,廣播裡面什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 1,0:45:44.74,0:45:46.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作已經出發去工作地點了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:45:47.29,0:45:47.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:45:47.95,0:45:51.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 從推測中的敵人續航力來看
Dialogue: 1,0:45:51.17,0:45:53.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,第一次空襲選擇九州是最好的
Dialogue: 1,0:45:47.95,0:45:53.25,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,1944年6月，美軍打贏菲律賓海戰（或稱馬里亞納海戰），為B-29轟炸機戰略轟炸日本本土提供了地理條件。\N吳市為當時B-29轟炸範圍內最重要的海軍基地。
Dialogue: 1,0:45:53.88,0:45:56.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,從這裡匆忙往山裡逃去
Dialogue: 1,0:45:58.09,0:45:59.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,停電而已
Dialogue: 1,0:46:02.80,0:46:04.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你別掉下來哦
Dialogue: 1,0:46:05.35,0:46:07.31,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,建物疎開：當時日本為了防止空襲時大火蔓延燒毀重要設施而設立的防火隔離帶。
Dialogue: 1,0:46:05.35,0:46:07.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,建築疏開啊
Dialogue: 1,0:46:08.35,0:46:10.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在市內擴建起了防火帶
Dialogue: 1,0:46:12.02,0:46:14.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 這裡的話應該不用擔心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:46:15.44,0:46:16.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真不容易啊
Dialogue: 1,0:46:17.32,0:46:19.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大家已經找到了搬家的地點了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:46:20.49,0:46:21.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:46:23.03,0:46:24.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不用謝
Dialogue: 1,0:46:25.87,0:46:27.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,柴火的話還有很多呢
Dialogue: 1,0:46:28.29,0:46:30.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我家被拆了
Dialogue: 1,0:46:32.58,0:46:35.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後 我們一家就搬到了下關市去了
Dialogue: 1,0:46:32.58,0:46:35.29,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,下關市：山口縣市名，位於本州最西端，距吳市約240千米。
Dialogue: 1,0:46:36.13,0:46:38.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,機會正好 我就跟他離婚了
Dialogue: 1,0:46:38.21,0:46:39.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:46:39.96,0:46:43.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不用擔心 我會找工作賺錢的
Dialogue: 1,0:46:44.30,0:46:46.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,要進入的人數變多了
Dialogue: 1,0:46:47.97,0:46:48.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這樣子嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:46:50.85,0:46:55.61,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50.193\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(337,160.618)}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:46:50.85,0:46:55.61,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(313,208.803)}年
Dialogue: 1,0:46:50.85,0:46:55.61,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60.232\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(335,303.166)}7
Dialogue: 1,0:46:50.85,0:46:55.61,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(309,348.565)}月
Dialogue: 1,0:46:55.02,0:46:57.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,昨天灰之峰上面也是響個不停呢
Dialogue: 1,0:46:58.27,0:47:00.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那樣子的地方都有大炮打過來呢
Dialogue: 1,0:47:00.99,0:47:02.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真危險啊
Dialogue: 1,0:47:03.66,0:47:05.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 1,0:47:04.24,0:47:05.28,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,那 先走了
Dialogue: 1,0:47:06.16,0:47:10.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 做出個挺好的防空洞不是麼
Dialogue: 1,0:47:12.25,0:47:15.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,即使是加班趕工做 也幹勁十足的嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:47:16.50,0:47:20.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,從姐姐家拿來的柱子和榻榻米真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 1,0:47:23.42,0:47:24.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作
Dialogue: 1,0:47:24.88,0:47:26.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你把它裝在這裡了呀
Dialogue: 1,0:47:27.26,0:47:28.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,無所謂了
Dialogue: 1,0:47:30.31,0:47:32.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後再收拾一下外面吧
Dialogue: 1,0:47:35.40,0:47:36.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作
Dialogue: 1,0:47:36.90,0:47:40.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這些泥土拿去田地裡可以麼
Dialogue: 1,0:47:41.32,0:47:42.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,拿去吧拿去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:47:43.03,0:47:43.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小心點
Dialogue: 1,0:47:44.65,0:47:46.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,呀 原來你在這裡呀
Dialogue: 1,0:47:48.28,0:47:49.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,來看船
Dialogue: 1,0:47:52.54,0:47:54.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,今天也有一大堆船呢
Dialogue: 1,0:47:54.75,0:47:56.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有兩艘大和號呢
Dialogue: 1,0:47:57.46,0:47:58.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,其中一艘是武藏
Dialogue: 1,0:47:54.75,0:47:58.71,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,武藏：大和級戰列艦2號艦，萊特灣海戰後泊於吳港。
Dialogue: 1,0:47:59.29,0:48:03.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,雖然戰艦有很多 航空母艦卻不在
Dialogue: 1,0:48:04.59,0:48:06.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 那個是利根號
Dialogue: 1,0:48:04.59,0:48:10.43,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,利根號：利根級重巡洋艦1號艦（航空巡洋艦），萊特灣海戰後泊於吳港。\N航空巡洋艦：特殊巡洋艦類別，為航空母艦與巡洋艦的混合體，尾部做為水上機彈射及降落甲板。
Dialogue: 1,0:48:06.63,0:48:10.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,尾部那裡沒有搭載炮台 是航空巡洋艦呢
Dialogue: 1,0:48:12.02,0:48:15.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真厲害啊 居然知道這麼多
Dialogue: 1,0:48:15.27,0:48:18.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 哥哥教會我的
Dialogue: 1,0:48:18.77,0:48:19.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 1,0:48:20.36,0:48:21.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也有稍微學過一些
Dialogue: 1,0:48:22.98,0:48:23.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,驅逐艦
Dialogue: 1,0:48:24.74,0:48:26.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 好像有什麼小小隻的過來了
Dialogue: 1,0:48:27.53,0:48:28.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那是內火艇
Dialogue: 1,0:48:27.53,0:48:28.91,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,內火艇：即配備有內燃機的艦載艇。
Dialogue: 1,0:48:30.87,0:48:32.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那麼我做為回報
Dialogue: 1,0:48:33.66,0:48:35.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,很大一片雲對吧
Dialogue: 1,0:48:36.33,0:48:38.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那叫做「砧狀積雨雲」
Dialogue: 1,0:48:39.63,0:48:41.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,看來要下大雨了
Dialogue: 1,0:48:45.59,0:48:46.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作
Dialogue: 1,0:48:46.34,0:48:49.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,總之先把那邊的東西放進防空洞裡吧
Dialogue: 1,0:48:58.73,0:48:59.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 1,0:49:07.03,0:49:08.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我自己來 我自己來
Dialogue: 1,0:49:09.95,0:49:11.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還真是喜歡軍艦呢
Dialogue: 1,0:49:12.74,0:49:14.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,聽晴美說的
Dialogue: 1,0:49:16.16,0:49:18.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不是我教晴美的
Dialogue: 1,0:49:18.87,0:49:19.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小久教的
Dialogue: 1,0:49:19.96,0:49:20.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,久？
Dialogue: 1,0:49:22.38,0:49:24.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 很喜歡軍艦的小久
Dialogue: 1,0:49:25.00,0:49:26.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,總有一天你也會見到他的
Dialogue: 1,0:49:27.51,0:49:28.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是這個
Dialogue: 1,0:49:29.05,0:49:30.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,叫「久夫」的人麼
Dialogue: 1,0:49:31.43,0:49:32.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:49:43.15,0:49:44.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我和這個人
Dialogue: 1,0:49:44.82,0:49:46.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在做這樣的事
Dialogue: 1,0:49:51.36,0:49:54.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好了 雨勢也變小了
Dialogue: 1,0:49:54.49,0:49:56.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,現在就回去吧
Dialogue: 1,0:49:57.04,0:49:58.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 1,0:49:58.08,0:50:02.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 都是夫婦了 能和睦相處是好事
Dialogue: 1,0:50:02.79,0:50:05.92,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 夫婦關係和睦是好事來的
Dialogue: 1,0:50:05.92,0:50:07.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,而且還有兩對
Dialogue: 1,0:50:07.13,0:50:08.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,徑子
Dialogue: 1,0:50:11.63,0:50:16.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一家人整整齊齊 開開心心地量身高
Dialogue: 1,0:50:17.10,0:50:18.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,莫非
Dialogue: 1,0:50:18.72,0:50:22.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐她的丈夫…
Dialogue: 1,0:50:22.44,0:50:26.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,難得擁有一副可以不參軍的瘦弱身體
Dialogue: 1,0:50:27.02,0:50:28.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,太瘦弱了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:50:30.11,0:50:33.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在父親進入工廠再就職的時候
Dialogue: 1,0:50:33.99,0:50:36.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐為了慶祝他而跑去買時鐘
Dialogue: 1,0:50:36.95,0:50:39.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就在那時候認識了那裡的少爺
Dialogue: 1,0:50:40.45,0:50:41.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後嫁給了他
Dialogue: 1,0:50:42.17,0:50:44.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,年輕夫婦兩人翻新了店面
Dialogue: 1,0:50:46.00,0:50:49.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是 徑子卻是那樣的性格
Dialogue: 1,0:50:49.80,0:50:52.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,與公公婆婆的關係又有很多矛盾
Dialogue: 1,0:50:52.76,0:50:54.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在丈夫去世後
Dialogue: 1,0:50:54.97,0:50:58.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對於店鋪的經營又有諸多問題
Dialogue: 1,0:50:58.85,0:51:03.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,隨後因為建築疏開 到最後什麼都沒剩下
Dialogue: 1,0:51:05.65,0:51:08.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因為久夫是黑村家的孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:51:09.36,0:51:11.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,被帶到了下關市去
Dialogue: 1,0:51:12.53,0:51:14.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,看起來應該是答應了
Dialogue: 1,0:51:15.87,0:51:19.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大家能夠開開心心地生活著就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:51:20.37,0:51:21.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:51:30.67,0:51:32.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我去看看那些蔬菜
Dialogue: 1,0:51:46.23,0:51:47.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在我認識這些東西之前
Dialogue: 1,0:51:48.31,0:51:50.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我已經好幾個月沒有畫過了
Dialogue: 1,0:51:51.23,0:51:53.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,基本都是在發呆呢
Dialogue: 1,0:51:58.32,0:51:59.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那是大和
Dialogue: 1,0:52:01.08,0:52:02.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這個是利根
Dialogue: 1,0:52:08.38,0:52:10.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個 我只是…
Dialogue: 1,0:52:12.00,0:52:13.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我… 好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:52:13.51,0:52:16.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我只是想給住在遠方的那孩子送去船的畫而已
Dialogue: 1,0:52:16.18,0:52:17.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這個女人的家是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:52:17.97,0:52:19.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,憲…憲兵大人
Dialogue: 1,0:52:20.60,0:52:22.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,畫了海岸線和軍艦身影的寫生
Dialogue: 1,0:52:23.72,0:52:24.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這是間諜行為
Dialogue: 1,0:52:25.10,0:52:26.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,擺出這幅表情
Dialogue: 1,0:52:26.69,0:52:30.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,使人分辨不出她擅長陰險精妙的計畫
Dialogue: 1,0:52:32.23,0:52:33.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這個女人的丈夫是
Dialogue: 1,0:52:34.15,0:52:37.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,海軍軍法會議所的下級記錄員吧
Dialogue: 1,0:52:37.70,0:52:41.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,很有可能這女人看準時機 在別人不注意的時候洩露軍事機密
Dialogue: 1,0:52:42.41,0:52:44.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有沒有察覺到暗號通信
Dialogue: 1,0:52:44.91,0:52:47.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在這女人的物品裡有沒有發現密碼表
Dialogue: 1,0:52:48.00,0:52:49.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還有透露這個女人背後關係的物品
Dialogue: 1,0:52:50.00,0:52:51.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有沒有？
Dialogue: 1,0:52:53.38,0:52:55.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這次先保留檢舉一事
Dialogue: 1,0:52:56.22,0:52:57.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,請時常保持雪亮的監視的眼睛
Dialogue: 1,0:52:58.34,0:53:00.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,即使是嫁進來了總歸是外人
Dialogue: 1,0:53:12.61,0:53:13.69,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 1,0:53:14.82,0:53:18.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 洗完的衣服一直乾放在那
Dialogue: 1,0:53:18.24,0:53:20.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 周作 那是因為
Dialogue: 1,0:53:20.20,0:53:22.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴被憲兵抓住…
Dialogue: 1,0:53:25.29,0:53:27.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 你過來一下
Dialogue: 1,0:53:35.46,0:53:38.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這麼小的話海岸線也畫不了了
Dialogue: 1,0:53:40.76,0:53:43.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原來你是很喜歡畫畫的人呀
Dialogue: 1,0:53:44.10,0:53:46.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,下次找機會畫我試試吧
Dialogue: 1,0:53:47.43,0:53:48.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 1,0:53:49.19,0:53:51.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我可能沒法畫得很好
Dialogue: 1,0:53:54.02,0:53:56.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴是間諜啊
Dialogue: 1,0:53:57.40,0:54:00.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作 你就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:54:00.40,0:54:03.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我們對著憲兵總覺得不好意思
Dialogue: 1,0:54:03.82,0:54:05.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,想笑又笑不了
Dialogue: 1,0:54:05.91,0:54:08.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,忍住的話反而會被懷疑
Dialogue: 1,0:54:11.87,0:54:13.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:54:13.75,0:54:16.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這孩子一旦專心入迷就注意不到周圍的東西了
Dialogue: 1,0:54:17.09,0:54:18.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,看上去一副老實的樣子
Dialogue: 1,0:54:18.38,0:54:20.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,反而又被當成是大智若愚的人
Dialogue: 1,0:54:20.97,0:54:22.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這…這個人啊
Dialogue: 1,0:54:22.43,0:54:25.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是會把「六點」回來聽成「紀錄」的人
Dialogue: 1,0:54:26.01,0:54:27.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,到底會盯上什麼機密啊
Dialogue: 1,0:54:27.93,0:54:29.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那群陸軍的笨蛋憲兵
Dialogue: 1,0:54:29.73,0:54:33.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,雖然不是很懂 突然變得好奇怪呢
Dialogue: 1,0:54:36.69,0:54:40.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大家能夠開開心心地生活著就好了
Dialogue: 1,0:54:40.74,0:54:42.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:54:42.03,0:54:43.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 1,0:54:43.91,0:54:46.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,父親呀 讓父親也聽一聽
Dialogue: 1,0:54:47.79,0:54:49.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就只有我笑不出來啊
Dialogue: 1,0:54:49.95,0:54:51.75,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,到底能有什麼企圖嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:54:52.21,0:54:54.25,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,根本什麼都不懂
Dialogue: 1,0:54:57.17,0:55:01.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,即使是戰爭時期 蟬鳴蝶飛依舊
Dialogue: 1,0:54:56.04,0:55:01.42,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50.193\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(337,160.618)\3c&H868686&}1944
Dialogue: 1,0:54:56.04,0:55:01.42,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(313,208.803)\3c&H868686&}年
Dialogue: 1,0:54:56.04,0:55:01.42,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60.232\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(335,303.166)\3c&H868686&}8
Dialogue: 1,0:54:56.04,0:55:01.42,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(309,348.565)\3c&H868686&}月
Dialogue: 1,0:55:01.47,0:55:03.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 1,0:55:00.67,0:55:07.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fs40.154\c&HD1DFE5&\fn方正稚艺_GBK\\pos(1079.058,191.038)} 通知\n 從八月開始砂糖的配給停止\n請更加節約使用
Dialogue: 1,0:55:05.64,0:55:07.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哎呀 連砂糖也
Dialogue: 1,0:55:08.64,0:55:11.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,六月空襲騷亂的時候
Dialogue: 1,0:55:11.18,0:55:14.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,還以為戰爭已經逼近我們的身邊
Dialogue: 1,0:55:15.06,0:55:17.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是現在到底是怎麼樣的情況呢
Dialogue: 1,0:55:20.69,0:55:22.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 1,0:55:22.19,0:55:24.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,晴美 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:55:24.16,0:55:25.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 1,0:55:25.82,0:55:27.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我在看螞蟻們
Dialogue: 1,0:55:29.24,0:55:31.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,到底延伸到哪裡去呢
Dialogue: 1,0:55:53.23,0:55:56.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,當下砂糖可是貴重物品啊
Dialogue: 1,0:56:03.24,0:56:06.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,把它藏在螞蟻們找不到的地方吧
Dialogue: 1,0:56:06.49,0:56:08.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 1,0:56:08.70,0:56:09.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,放哪裡好
Dialogue: 1,0:56:14.16,0:56:15.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,0:56:16.54,0:56:18.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我想著如果
Dialogue: 1,0:56:18.38,0:56:21.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,放在水上螞蟻們就不會接近了
Dialogue: 1,0:56:30.51,0:56:33.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,拿去吧 去黑市買回來
Dialogue: 1,0:56:38.10,0:56:39.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,走著和平常不同的路
Dialogue: 1,0:56:43.07,0:56:44.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,請慢用
Dialogue: 1,0:56:49.70,0:56:51.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,按道理應該沒有東西可賣才對
Dialogue: 1,0:56:52.24,0:56:53.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,為什麼會有這麼多人
Dialogue: 1,0:56:59.08,0:57:02.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這是臺灣米 剛收成的
Dialogue: 1,0:56:58.62,0:57:03.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正毡笔黑_GBK\fs50.193\bord0\c&H6C6F73&\frz5.559\pos(297.058,98.683)}下次進貨時間預定在月底
Dialogue: 1,0:57:03.88,0:57:06.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,或者內地米也可以拿到貨哦
Dialogue: 1,0:57:08.68,0:57:11.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,田裡明明是禁止種西瓜的才對
Dialogue: 1,0:57:13.56,0:57:15.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼都有
Dialogue: 1,0:57:19.65,0:57:22.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就像是戰爭前的暑假一樣
Dialogue: 1,0:57:23.57,0:57:25.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,砂糖一斤二十圓
Dialogue: 1,0:57:26.07,0:57:29.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,配…配給的五十倍以上
Dialogue: 1,0:57:29.28,0:57:31.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,現在不買只會越來越貴
Dialogue: 1,0:57:32.28,0:57:37.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,母親的私房錢加上這個月的生活費加起來才二十五圓
Dialogue: 1,0:57:37.75,0:57:40.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,柿種
Dialogue: 1,0:57:43.67,0:57:47.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,現在砂糖變成了一百五十圓左右
Dialogue: 1,0:57:48.05,0:57:51.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一百圓也買不到牛奶糖之類的
Dialogue: 1,0:57:51.51,0:57:56.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,買三雙襪子的話差不多要一千圓了
Dialogue: 1,0:57:57.35,0:58:00.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在這樣的國家裡還能活的下去嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:58:06.48,0:58:09.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,等下 這裡到底是哪裡
Dialogue: 1,0:58:10.20,0:58:11.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯？長之木？
Dialogue: 1,0:58:12.11,0:58:13.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,海軍墓地那兒嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:58:13.82,0:58:15.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 那是長迫呀
Dialogue: 1,0:58:15.74,0:58:17.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那邊麼？
Dialogue: 1,0:58:17.37,0:58:18.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這邊才對吧
Dialogue: 1,0:58:34.18,0:58:34.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:58:39.81,0:58:40.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 1,0:58:41.48,0:58:42.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,西瓜
Dialogue: 1,0:58:43.98,0:58:44.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,牛奶糖？
Dialogue: 1,0:58:46.36,0:58:47.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,迷路了？
Dialogue: 1,0:58:49.28,0:58:50.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,明明是大人了？
Dialogue: 1,0:58:51.36,0:58:52.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你是從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 1,0:58:53.28,0:58:54.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,長之木
Dialogue: 1,0:58:55.24,0:58:58.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大姐姐 沒人能告訴我回家的路
Dialogue: 1,0:58:59.16,0:59:00.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大家都有香香的味道
Dialogue: 1,0:59:01.37,0:59:03.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這裡是龍宮城還是什麼地方嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:59:04.42,0:59:08.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,長之木的話 在那裡拐角 走到郵政局
Dialogue: 1,0:59:09.17,0:59:09.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 1,0:59:10.76,0:59:11.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,等一下下
Dialogue: 1,0:59:13.43,0:59:16.14,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐 問個問題
Dialogue: 1,0:59:21.10,0:59:23.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沿著這裡走 然後走出那裡
Dialogue: 1,0:59:23.73,0:59:27.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在郵政局前的那個拐角往右走就是了
Dialogue: 1,0:59:27.94,0:59:29.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,非常謝謝你
Dialogue: 1,0:59:30.69,0:59:34.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這裡的人其實都不是很熟悉路
Dialogue: 1,0:59:34.45,0:59:38.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大部分都是外地人 基本沒走出過這個門
Dialogue: 1,0:59:39.20,0:59:41.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你也是廣島南部的…
Dialogue: 1,0:59:42.25,0:59:43.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,海邊嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:59:43.58,0:59:45.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是的 你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 1,0:59:46.13,0:59:47.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你說的話
Dialogue: 1,0:59:48.46,0:59:49.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,江波那邊嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:59:49.46,0:59:51.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 草津那裡
Dialogue: 1,0:59:51.46,0:59:52.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,草津
Dialogue: 1,0:59:53.42,0:59:56.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,每年都會在奶奶家吃西瓜呢
Dialogue: 1,0:59:56.97,0:59:59.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我家裡因為很窮
Dialogue: 1,0:59:59.35,1:00:01.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,只能啃別人吃剩的瓜皮
Dialogue: 1,1:00:02.64,1:00:04.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有一次好心人給了我一個
Dialogue: 1,1:00:05.56,1:00:07.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,吃上了紅色的部分呢
Dialogue: 1,1:00:08.61,1:00:10.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,很久遠的事情了
Dialogue: 1,1:00:11.48,1:00:13.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,話說回來你畫得真好呢
Dialogue: 1,1:00:14.24,1:00:17.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,看起來 那個…
Dialogue: 1,1:00:18.57,1:00:19.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小事一樁
Dialogue: 1,1:00:20.41,1:00:22.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,另外還有什麼想我畫的都跟我說吧
Dialogue: 1,1:00:22.66,1:00:24.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,薄荷糖　蕨菜餅
Dialogue: 1,1:00:25.16,1:00:26.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,薄荷糖…
Dialogue: 1,1:00:26.62,1:00:30.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後就是冰淇淋 加上威化餅的
Dialogue: 1,1:00:31.13,1:00:31.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,威化？
Dialogue: 1,1:00:32.34,1:00:35.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不知道麼？ 你沒去過咖啡廳麼？
Dialogue: 1,1:00:35.09,1:00:36.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,玲
Dialogue: 1,1:00:36.34,1:00:38.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不要再閒聊了
Dialogue: 1,1:00:38.76,1:00:40.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我必須回去了
Dialogue: 1,1:00:41.43,1:00:43.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,下次我再給你畫好了
Dialogue: 1,1:00:45.98,1:00:46.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 1,1:00:47.56,1:00:49.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這種地方還是不要來第二次
Dialogue: 1,1:00:53.23,1:00:55.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,又會再次迷路的
Dialogue: 1,1:01:16.51,1:01:17.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真晚啊
Dialogue: 1,1:01:17.84,1:01:21.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,說了去市場 我就想是不是回來的時候迷路了
Dialogue: 1,1:01:22.85,1:01:23.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 1,1:01:24.14,1:01:27.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,說到咖啡廳裡帶威化餅的冰淇淋
Dialogue: 1,1:01:27.85,1:01:29.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你知道是什麼東西麼
Dialogue: 1,1:01:29.27,1:01:30.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼 你沒聽過嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:01:31.52,1:01:34.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個啊 甜甜的涼涼的
Dialogue: 1,1:01:34.61,1:01:37.86,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,蘸上脆脆的像仙貝一樣的東西吃
Dialogue: 1,1:01:38.24,1:01:40.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那真是…
Dialogue: 1,1:01:40.82,1:01:41.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 1,1:01:44.79,1:01:47.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,久違地說起甜食的話題
Dialogue: 1,1:01:47.33,1:01:50.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喝口水都變甜了
Dialogue: 1,1:01:53.54,1:02:00.05,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50.193\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(337,160.618)\3c&H464646&}1944
Dialogue: 1,1:01:53.54,1:02:00.05,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(313,208.803)\3c&H464646&}年
Dialogue: 1,1:01:53.54,1:02:00.05,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs60.232\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(335,303.166)\3c&H464646&}9
Dialogue: 1,1:01:53.54,1:02:00.05,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(309,348.565)\3c&H464646&}月
Dialogue: 1,1:01:57.51,1:01:58.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,天還很熱
Dialogue: 1,1:02:00.55,1:02:02.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,北條家的媳婦
Dialogue: 1,1:02:02.55,1:02:03.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有打給你的電話
Dialogue: 1,1:02:05.35,1:02:07.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,來了 給我的電話嗎
Dialogue: 1,1:02:11.27,1:02:12.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 這個這個
Dialogue: 1,1:02:14.02,1:02:15.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 1,1:02:15.61,1:02:17.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,受到蒙羞的人是周作
Dialogue: 1,1:02:17.32,1:02:18.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你啊 就這個樣子出門…
Dialogue: 1,1:02:28.91,1:02:31.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就在附近 稍微走一走吧
Dialogue: 1,1:02:31.83,1:02:34.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然後 GKF的情況如何
Dialogue: 1,1:02:31.83,1:02:34.96,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,注: GKF指日本海軍南西方面艦隊，菲律賓海戰時前線艦隊之一。
Dialogue: 1,1:02:35.21,1:02:36.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,現在是很空閒的樣子
Dialogue: 1,1:02:36.42,1:02:37.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 1,1:02:37.50,1:02:39.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 先去喝點冰啤酒吧
Dialogue: 1,1:02:55.77,1:02:58.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作 我給你送筆記本來了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:04.74,1:03:05.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 1,1:03:06.45,1:03:08.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,塗得好白啊 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 1,1:03:09.45,1:03:11.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,會不會很奇怪呀
Dialogue: 1,1:03:12.25,1:03:14.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒事 精神就好
Dialogue: 1,1:03:14.83,1:03:16.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 1,1:03:17.79,1:03:18.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,工作怎麼辦
Dialogue: 1,1:03:19.21,1:03:22.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,明明不是很急 卻特意幫我把筆記本拿過來
Dialogue: 1,1:03:23.51,1:03:26.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你說過到鎮上買東西很開心對吧
Dialogue: 1,1:03:30.64,1:03:31.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:32.10,1:03:33.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,果然身體有什麼…
Dialogue: 1,1:03:33.52,1:03:35.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在偷偷樂而已啦
Dialogue: 1,1:03:41.49,1:03:43.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,本來還想著看電影
Dialogue: 1,1:03:45.86,1:03:48.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,剛好有艘大船回港了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:50.99,1:03:52.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒辦法 只能讓給他們看了
Dialogue: 1,1:03:53.54,1:03:55.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,雖然有點可惜 還是等下一次吧
Dialogue: 1,1:03:59.04,1:04:00.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴？
Dialogue: 1,1:04:00.59,1:04:05.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小學同年級的有成為水兵的
Dialogue: 1,1:04:05.80,1:04:08.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,見到了不知道要怎麼辦好…
Dialogue: 1,1:04:08.39,1:04:10.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,普通地打招呼不就行了
Dialogue: 1,1:04:11.81,1:04:14.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果現在跟以前認識的人見了面的話
Dialogue: 1,1:04:14.60,1:04:18.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我會不會就從夢裡醒來了呢
Dialogue: 1,1:04:18.90,1:04:19.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,夢…
Dialogue: 1,1:04:20.11,1:04:23.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,住所跟姓氏都變了 淨是讓人為難的事
Dialogue: 1,1:04:24.24,1:04:27.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過即使如此 能有周作對我好
Dialogue: 1,1:04:27.49,1:04:29.28,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,而且還交到了朋友
Dialogue: 1,1:04:30.08,1:04:33.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯… 現在醒來的話就不有趣了
Dialogue: 1,1:04:33.70,1:04:36.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,如果現在的我就是真正的我 那就挺好的
Dialogue: 1,1:04:36.62,1:04:37.83,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 1,1:04:39.13,1:04:41.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,過去的事 沒選擇的道路
Dialogue: 1,1:04:42.38,1:04:45.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,都跟醒來時結束的夢沒兩樣
Dialogue: 1,1:04:45.97,1:04:48.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 選擇了你
Dialogue: 1,1:04:48.84,1:04:51.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,對我來說很可能是最好的選擇了
Dialogue: 1,1:04:53.22,1:04:56.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,只不過你好像有點瘦了 真讓人擔心
Dialogue: 1,1:04:56.81,1:05:00.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,說起來 最近好像沒什麼胃口…
Dialogue: 1,1:05:07.74,1:05:09.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,給 2人份
Comment: 0,1:05:07.90,1:05:08.95,kono-text-jp,,0,0,0,,#0
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.63,1:05:27.30,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,從左到右：蕨菜餅、薄荷糖、西瓜
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.63,1:05:26.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,畫得真好
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.84,1:05:29.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,謝謝你專門跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.51,1:05:35.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是去完醫院順路過來的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.52,1:05:38.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,醫院？哪裡不舒服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.69,1:05:40.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.15,1:05:43.06,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.23,1:05:45.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,畫得真像 西瓜
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.69,1:05:48.74,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,蕨菜餅 薄荷糖
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.20,1:05:53.50,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,旁邊註文：冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.70,1:05:53.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.92,1:06:07.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,其實 那是冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.30,1:06:10.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什麼 這是冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.72,1:06:16.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我沒見過那麼高級的東西
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.14,1:06:18.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我才該說抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.06,1:06:24.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我只上過半年小學 雖說片假名勉強能認出來
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.23,1:06:28.19,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但平假名就完全不會讀了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.94,1:06:39.70,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,身許票：一種個人身份證明，一般縫在胸前，由本人寫上姓名年齡籍貫住址血型等資訊，\N目的是在空襲後能迅速查明受難者的身份資訊。
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.94,1:06:34.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那你怎麼寫自己的身份牌呢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.53,1:06:39.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不要緊 有位恩客幫我寫好了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.16,1:06:43.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這樣就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.29,1:06:48.38,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,原來你叫白木玲
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.63,1:06:54.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那麼 我也得做個遲到的自我介紹了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.23,1:07:08.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,ホー
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.78,1:07:10.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,ヂ…ヂャウ？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.71,1:07:23.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你叫鈴對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.23,1:07:23.87,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,此處是日語諧音，三部分發音合起來就是「北條鈴」
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.96,1:07:26.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.75,1:07:33.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 謝謝你 這畫我會珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.80,1:07:35.80,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,用不著客氣
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.72,1:07:43.27,kono-comments,,0,0,0,,曲名為「どうじゃね元気かね」，是由古賀政男作曲的戰時歌謠
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.72,1:07:43.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,做人要勤快
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.44,1:07:46.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個 玲
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.82,1:07:53.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我聽了接生婆的話 去醫院院婦科做了檢查
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.82,1:07:56.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你懷孕了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.28,1:08:02.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也這麼想 但好象是由於營養不足和環境變化
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.20,1:08:05.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,造成了月事不調
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.92,1:08:10.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這裡有不少姐妹也和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.30,1:08:12.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.84,1:08:17.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,脫脂棉也好布也好 如今連紙都貴重起來了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.64,1:08:20.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嘛 這倒也是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.47,1:08:27.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,本來周作和家裡人本來還盼著聽好消息呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.35,1:08:29.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.56,1:08:31.77,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是我丈夫
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.19,1:08:34.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,其實你也盼著好消息吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.65,1:08:36.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.07,1:08:41.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我的母親每次生了孩子都會掉牙齒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.66,1:08:46.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,最後她就死於生孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.46,1:08:49.71,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這事有什麼可盼望的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.21,1:08:56.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,說起來是怪嚇人的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.01,1:08:58.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.59,1:09:02.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,男人們上戰場不也是冒著生命危險嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.72,1:09:05.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我們女人也要盡自己的義務
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.31,1:09:06.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,義務？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.60,1:09:12.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,給家裡留下合格的繼承人 就是妻子的義務
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.73,1:09:15.53,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但也沒法保證生下的一定是男孩呀
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.11,1:09:19.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那就一直生到生出男孩止
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.57,1:09:22.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但也沒法保證他是合格的呀
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.45,1:09:24.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那就多生幾個 以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.12,1:09:27.79,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那生起來可就沒完了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.91,1:09:31.25,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嗯 有道理
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.46,1:09:36.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,假如妻子沒有盡到那個義務會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.67,1:09:39.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,會被趕回娘家
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.68,1:09:41.59,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,回到娘家會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.76,1:09:43.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那個嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.56,1:09:48.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,會被鬼哥哥揍一頓吧 不過他還在戰場上
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.06,1:09:52.94,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我爸媽倒是已經習慣這種事了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.11,1:09:55.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也還可以待在挺身隊裡
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.98,1:09:57.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,和妹妹澄一起
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.15,1:10:01.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那麼 這事有那麼可怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.21,1:10:14.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不過有個孩子也算有個依靠
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.42,1:10:18.34,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,而且還會很可愛
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.46,1:10:19.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,實在不行還能賣了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.84,1:10:26.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,女孩能賣個好價錢 也不用擔心家業
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.35,1:10:29.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,想生就生吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.89,1:10:36.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我真傻 到底為了什麼而煩惱呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.27,1:10:38.44,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.74,1:10:48.70,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎 就算是被賣掉的孩子 也會有辦法活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.83,1:10:54.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這個世界上不是誰都總是沒有歸宿的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.46,1:10:56.63,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你說呢 鈴
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.21,1:11:01.17,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 玲
Comment: 0,1:11:12.23,1:11:14.73,kono-text-jp,,0,0,0,,#1
Dialogue: 1,1:11:12.02,1:11:14.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,畢竟早上白白地多吃了那麼多
Dialogue: 1,1:11:14.44,1:11:16.40,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大概這個量應該夠了吧
Comment: 0,1:11:14.81,1:11:16.73,kono-text-jp,,0,0,0,,#0
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.36,1:11:21.36,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,只有最上層的清水
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.87,1:11:29.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,秋風漸起 警報也響得越來越頻繁了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.87,1:11:33.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,秋天已至 收好夏天的被褥
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.71,1:11:35.58,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,換上冬天的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.79,1:11:40.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,順便安頓好小林伯父家送來的行李物品
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.30,1:11:45.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大家都辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.34,1:11:47.60,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鈴 你也來喝口茶吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.72,1:11:49.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.89,1:11:54.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這下
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.60,1:11:57.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就算我家被燒了也不用為生活發愁了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.02,1:12:01.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,連牙刷和內衣都備妥了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.69,1:12:06.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這不是我們家的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.61,1:12:08.24,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也沒見過
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.16,1:12:11.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,應該是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.54,1:12:14.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你不會連自己的嫁妝都記不清了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.41,1:12:16.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.59,1:12:25.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,阿鈴真是個好媳婦啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.84,1:12:28.97,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,手腳勤快
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.10,1:12:30.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,脾氣又好
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.89,1:12:35.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,多虧了你 感覺周作也變得開朗些了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.98,1:12:46.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,讓他趁早打消那些胡思亂想的怪念頭
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.28,1:12:50.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,定下心來好好跟阿鈴過日子
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.70,1:12:53.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,這才像話嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.30,1:13:05.26,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我該去翻被子了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.35,1:13:14.81,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,怎麼 她還害羞了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.89,1:13:17.64,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我敢說重要的話她一句都沒聽進去
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.89,1:13:20.61,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我倒希望她沒聽進去
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.77,1:13:22.65,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,瞧我出的這一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.78,1:13:26.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你瞧 鈴
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.40,1:13:30.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,夏天和秋天都都有紅蜻蜓
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.45,1:13:31.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是是不一樣的紅色
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.99,1:13:34.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真的吔
Dialogue: 1,1:13:36.00,1:13:40.75,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50.193\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\3c&H868686&\pos(220.43,159.48)}1944
